And just thinking about TV and
all those different sources

00:00:31.390 --> 00:00:36.110 align:middle line:84%
of what we see, is that can
you imagine if just a fraction

00:00:36.110 --> 00:00:38.400 align:middle line:84%
of that would be
spent on the issues

00:00:38.400 --> 00:00:42.720 align:middle line:84%
that we've been talking about,
about creating this new dream

00:00:42.720 --> 00:00:45.460 align:middle line:84%
