sustainable, spiritually

00:00:45.460 --> 00:00:47.450 align:middle line:90%
fulfilling and socially just.

00:00:47.450 --> 00:00:51.070 align:middle line:84%
And so if we can imagine that
happening-- and the reality,

00:00:51.070 --> 00:00:54.220 align:middle line:84%
