So I repeat, this is your home.

00:01:11.390 --> 00:01:12.860 align:middle line:90%
It's the only one you got.

00:01:12.860 --> 00:01:14.060 align:middle line:90%
Cherish it, protect it.

00:01:14.060 --> 00:01:16.860 align:middle line:84%
It's the only one
you're going to get.

00:01:16.860 --> 00:01:18.670 align:middle line:10%
These guys, they're
your neighbors.

00:01:18.670 --> 00:01:19.720 align:middle line:90%
They ain't going away.

00:01:19.720 --> 00:01:20.490 align:middle line:90%
They ain't leaving.

00:01:20.490 --> 00:01:21.940 align:middle line:90%
You have to get along with them.

00:01:21.940 --> 00:01:23.580 align:middle line:90%
So you have to learn to share.

00:01:23.580 --> 00:01:24.920 align:middle line:90%
You have to get along.

00:01:24.920 --> 00:01:26.520 align:middle line:90%
You have to learn to get along.

00:01:26.520 --> 00:01:29.301 align:middle line:84%
Because they are your neighbors,
they're not going away.

00:01:29.301 --> 00:01:30.000 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:32.895 align:middle line:84%
All this stuff, the animals,
the waters, the sky, the ground,

00:01:32.895 --> 00:01:36.060 align:middle line:84%
the bugs, the fish,
the tacos, the people,

00:01:36.060 --> 00:01:37.310 align:middle line:90%
they're all connected.

00:01:37.310 --> 00:01:38.560 align:middle line:90%
Everything is connected.

00:01:38.560 --> 00:01:40.140 align:middle line:90%
They all depend on one another.

00:01:40.140 --> 00:01:42.310 align:middle line:84%
If you ignore that,
you're doomed.

00:01:42.310 --> 00:01:43.466 align:middle line:84%
Repeat, doomed.
OK.

00:01:43.466 --> 00:01:45.310 align:middle line:84%
So listen up.
It's all one.

00:01:45.310 --> 00:01:47.170 align:middle line:90%
Not two worlds, not three.

00:01:47.170 --> 00:01:48.640 align:middle line:90%
One, just one.

00:01:48.640 --> 00:01:49.440 align:middle line:90%
So get it in gear.

